surprisingly old-fashioned references--to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Charles Kindleberger</ENAMEX>'s classic <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1978</TIMEX>
book <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Manias, Panics, and Crashes</ENAMEX> , and even to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Walter Bagehot</ENAMEX>'s
<ENAMEX TYPE="FAC">Lombard Street</ENAMEX> (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1873</TIMEX>). <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Asia</ENAMEX>'s debacle, a growing number of us now think,
