<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX> of those <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> who believes that the <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Asian</ENAMEX> crisis will or even can cause a
